== Awards and nominations == Several of Michelle Mohabeer's film have earned international awards and [[honorable mention]]s at [[film festival]]s across the [[Earth|globe]]; these films include ''Child-play'', ''Coconut/Cane & Cutlass'' and E''xposure''. ''Exposure'' in particular has received much recognition, in particular the [[National Film Board of Canada|NFB]]'s Five Feminist Minutes Award.<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":14">{{Citation|last=Armstrong|first=Mary|title=Five feminist minutes|date=1990-01-01|url=http://www.worldcat.org/title/five-feminist-minutes/oclc/606938904|last2=Hubert|last3=National Film Board of Canada|last4=NFB:Studio D|last5=NFB:Regards de femmes|first2=Nicole|publisher=National Film Board of Canada ; Moving Images [distributor]|language=English|accessdate=2016-10-14}}</ref><ref name=":15">{{Cite web|url=http://people.wcsu.edu/mccarneyh/fva/M/MohabeerM_vita.html|title=Michelle Mohabeer Vita|website=people.wcsu.edu|access-date=2016-10-26}}</ref> {| class="wikitable" !Year !Organization !Awards !Film |- |1989 |[[National Film Board of Canada]] -Studio D |5 Feminist Minutes Award<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name=":15" /> |''Exposure'' |- |1990 |Black Film/Video Network |Award of Recognition<ref name=":15" /> |''Exposure'' |- |1991 |41st [[Berlin International Film Festival]] |Official Selection Certificate<ref name=":15" /> |''Exposure'' |- |1994 |32nd [[Ann Arbor Film Festival]] |Isabella Liddell Art Award of Excellence<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":15" /> |''Coconut/Cane & Cutlass'' |- |1994 |Curve magazine, [[San Francisco]] |Top Ten Independent Short Film<ref name=":15" /> |''Coconut/Cane & Cutlass'' |- |1995 |10th [[Turin International Film Festival]] |Special Mention in Documentary Category<ref name=":15" /> |''Coconut/Cane & Cutlass'' |- |1998 |11th Annual Images Film & Video Festival |Honourable Mention Certificate for Best Direction<ref name=":15" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.imagesfestival.com/images/festival/12.pdf|title=Images '98 Festival of Independent Film and Video|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|access-date=2016-10-26}}</ref> |''Child-Play'' |}
