The '''Institute of Molecular Biology and Genetics of the [[National Academy of Sciences of Ukraine]]''' (IMBG of the NASU) is a scientific research organisation in the [[Ukraine|Ukrainian]] city of [[Kiev]]. Founded in 1973 as a branch of the National Academy of Sciences of Ukraine, the institute specialises in [[genomics]], [[proteomics]], [[bioinformatics]], [[genetic engineering]] and cellular engineering.
